<div class="map-card glass-panel">
  <div class="map-header">
    <h3>🗺️ Peta Dampak Pelatihan GASING Nusantara</h3>
    <p>Sentuh atau klik titik pada peta untuk melihat bukti nyata perubahan numerasi anak-anak bangsa di daerah tersebut.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Centered Search Autocomplete Container -->
  <div class="map-search-container max-w-md mx-auto mb-6 relative">
    <input type="text" id="map-search-input" placeholder="🔍 Cari Kabupaten atau Provinsi..." class="map-search-input" autocomplete="off" style="padding-right: 40px;" />
    <button id="map-search-clear-btn" class="map-search-clear-btn hidden" type="button">✕</button>
    <div id="map-search-results" class="map-search-results hidden"></div>
